{"tid":1894764,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔又贏，每名永久居民1萬元，4月派錢","createTime":"2020-02-24T06:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T01:57:37.000Z","uid":213877,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"12ca810105d01215753779195634912370d024a4","tid":1894764,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T06:28:19.000Z","msg":"因應疫情對經濟民生造成影響，澳門政府提早年度派錢安排，由平常的7月起發放，提早至4月起。<br />\n<br />\n所有於2019年12月31日持有有效或可續期澳門居民身分證的居民，可獲發年度現金分享，每名永久居民1萬元，非永久居民6000元，受惠的永久居民約68萬人，非永久居民約4.8萬人，涉及的預算總開支約71億元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200224/_2020022412443947792.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200224%2F_2020022412443947792.jpg&h=dc734ac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1707970/即時-港聞-疫情影響經濟-澳門提早至4月派錢每人1萬\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1707970%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F-%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E6%8F%90%E6%97%A9%E8%87%B34%E6%9C%88%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2%E6%AF%8F%E4%BA%BA1%E8%90%AC&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpArXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=fbbbcb7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1707970%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F-%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E6%8F%90%E6%97%A9%E8%87%B34%E6%9C%88%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2%E6%AF%8F%E4%BA%BA1%E8%90%AC&h=6d327662\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1707970/即時-港聞-疫情影響經濟-澳門提早至4月派錢每人1萬</a>"},{"pid":"8d0367156e6bcd3fdd2b3772aab95b96955cb729","tid":1894764,"uid":69231,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T06:28:55.000Z","msg":"這些機會..."},{"pid":"5afc4519d45bb0a482f4cf13488b696cb3a1808f","tid":1894764,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite